  <entry>
    <title>数学笔记</title>
    <link href="/2026/06/26/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/"/>
    <url>/2026/06/26/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="逆元"><a href="#逆元" class="headerlink" title="逆元"></a>逆元</h3><p>$a^{-1}$ 称为 $a$ 的乘法逆元<br>令 $$x &#x3D; a^{-1}$$<br>$$xa \equiv 1 \pmod{p}$$<br>由费马小定理 $$a^{p-1} \equiv 1 \pmod{p}$$<br>得 $$a^{p-2} \cdot a \equiv 1 \pmod{p}$$<br>所以 $$x&#x3D;a^{p-2}$$</p><h4 id="线性求乘法逆元"><a href="#线性求乘法逆元" class="headerlink" title="线性求乘法逆元"></a>线性求乘法逆元</h4><p>$$p&#x3D;ki+r$$<br>$$ki+r \equiv 0 \pmod{p}$$<br>同乘 $i^{-1}$ $r^{-1}$<br>$$k \cdot r^{-1}+i^{-1} \equiv 0 \pmod{p}$$<br>$$i^{-1} \equiv -k \cdot r^{-1} \pmod{p}$$<br>$$i^{-1} \equiv -\lfloor \frac{p}{i} \rfloor \cdot (p\mod i)^{-1} \pmod{p}$$</p><figure class="highlight q"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs q"><span class="hljs-built_in">inv</span>[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]=<span class="hljs-built_in">inv</span>[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>for(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)  <span class="hljs-built_in">inv</span>[i]=(p-p/i)*<span class="hljs-built_in">inv</span>[p%i]%p;<br>for(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)  <span class="hljs-built_in">inv</span>[i]=<span class="hljs-built_in">inv</span>[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]*<span class="hljs-built_in">inv</span>[i]%p;  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
